Interface RemoteAccess

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    _FederatedDirectoryService, _FederatedInfoEngineService, _ProxyGroup, AttachmentQueryCommands, Authentication, ChangeDirectiveQueryCommands, ChangeItemQueryCommands, ChangeStatusCalculator, CINValidityPostUpgradeUtility, ClassificationUtility, ComponentUtility, CreateAndEditModelGetter, CreateAndEditWizBean, DefaultProposedSolutionHandler, DeleteObjectCommands, EffConfigSpecAssistant, EffGroupAssistant, FederatedDirectoryService, FederatedInfoEngineService, HTTPServer, LoadHelper, PagingSessionHelper, PrefSearchService, PrefsRegistry, PromotionNoticeWorkflowHelper, ProxyGroup, RelatedChangesQueryCommands, ReplicaLoader, ReportTemplateQueryHelper, StackTraceUtil, SubmissionCommands, TrainingRecordCommands, UpgradeContainerTemplateHelper, WorkSetCompServiceCommand, WorkSetManagementHelper, WVSLoggerHelper

    public interface RemoteAccess
    Interface used to tag classes that are available for remote access via a method server. The method server's invoke method can only be used to invoke methods on classes tagged for remote access.

    Supported API: true
